    <h2 style="color: #1170C3; margin-top: 2.5rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3 style="color: #1A1A2E;">How much should a church budget for Facebook ads?</h3>
    <p style="line-height: 1.8; color: #333;">
      Most churches can start seeing meaningful results with $5-$20 per day. A monthly budget of $150-$600 is a solid starting point. As you learn what works, scale your budget toward the campaigns producing the best engagement and responses.
    </p>

